STYLE DEVELOPMENT: Unique synthesis of two distinct Rio lineages - São Bento Grande (Djalma/Artur Emídio Bahian tradition) and Angola/São Bento Pequeno (Leopoldina/Quinzinho carioca malandro tradition).

