- Augusto Salvador Brito (Canhão)

POSSIBLE ACADEMIC CAREER (requires verification):
If Luciano José Costa Figueiredo the capoeirista is the same as the veterinarian:
- UFBA Veterinary Medicine degree: 1971
- UFMG Master''s: 1974
