- Swiss locations: Baden (HQ), Aarau, Chur, Lucerne, Schaffhausen, St. Gallen, Winterthur, Wetzikon, Zofingen
- International: Monza/Trieste (Italy), Ravensburg (Germany), Rio de Janeiro (Brazil)
