TRAINING COMPANIONS at Waldemar''s roda (per João Grande 1989 testimony):
- Evanir, Tatá, Bom Cabelo (José Cabelo Bom), Chita, Macário, Sete Molas (Waldemar)

MEDIA APPEARANCES:
